inal=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-cd9e4b94c58aa845c9720e11b76ade5f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-cd9e4b94c58aa845c9720e11b76ade5f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"cXqiKFH1\">能够跟踪各种知识的复习</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2de09dba3a7b9af5abee9edef9a4951_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-f31a8430bcd8e9419eb271b8f928e878\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a12122b4eb9e02a373c5b5d35622b702_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f2de09dba3a7b9af5abee9edef9a4951_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-f31a8430bcd8e9419eb271b8f928e878\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a12122b4eb9e02a373c5b5d35622b702_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f2de09dba3a7b9af5abee9edef9a4951_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2de09dba3a7b9af5abee9edef9a4951_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"7BvcawpT\">如果题主想要试试这个软件，可以看看我写的教程</p><a data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"internal\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61</span><span class=\"invisible\">564332</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><p data-pid=\"M-UuQwJ8\">希望对大家有所帮助。</p>",
